OL,3,CSteve Tandy: 'There's no magic wand or
OL,4,Cquick fix ` I believe in Welsh talent'
OL,6,FNew head coach Steve Tandy says Wales
OL,7,Fmust show ambition to restore national
OL,8,Fpride after sliding down the world
OL,9,Forder.
OL,11,FTonmawr-born Tandy, a former Ospreys
OL,12,Fplayer and coach, has ended a six-year
OL,13,Fstay as Scotland defence coach to
OL,14,Freturn home to Wales.
