OL,3,CSteve Tandy: 'There's no magic wand or
OL,4,Cquick fix ` I believe in Welsh talent'
OL,6,F"So, it's a feeling of absolute pride
OL,7,Fand an honour."
OL,9,FWales were 2019 World Cup semi-
OL,10,Ffinalists under Warren Gatland and
OL,11,FWayne Pivac's side won the 2021 Six
OL,12,FNations Championship.
OL,14,FBut Pivac's reign quickly unravelled
OL,15,Fand Gatland's return ` the Kiwi had
OL,16,Foverseen a glorious chapter between
OL,17,F2007 and 2019 ` produced no upturn in
OL,18,Ffortunes, with his departure coming
OL,19,Fduring the 2025 Six Nations in
OL,20,FFebruary.
