OL,3,CSteve Tandy: 'There's no magic wand or
OL,4,Cquick fix ` I believe in Welsh talent'
OL,6,FThe Welsh Rugby Union has stated it
OL,7,Fwants to see Wales in the top five in
OL,8,Fthe world by 2029.
OL,10,FBut is that a realistic target given
OL,11,Fthe problems facing the Welsh game at
OL,12,Fa time when four regions could be cut
OL,13,Fto two and the talent pool is shallow
OL,14,Fcompared to rival nations?
OL,16,FTandy said: "I believe in the talent
OL,17,Fwe have in Wales, to get us to where
OL,18,Fwe want to go.
