OL,3,CSteve Tandy: 'There's no magic wand or
OL,4,Cquick fix ` I believe in Welsh talent'
OL,6,F"There's not going to be a magic wand
OL,7,For a quick fix and then it all
OL,8,Fchanges, but I do believe in the
OL,9,Fpathway.
OL,11,F"Ultimately you want to have ambition.
OL,12,FWe want to have ambition to meet those
OL,13,Ftargets, but ultimately there's a
OL,14,Fprocess to get to that as well.
OL,16,F"We have to build performances
OL,17,Fincrementally. From campaign to
OL,18,Fcampaign we have to be better and
OL,19,Flooking at how we can build that
OL,20,Fperformance through the exciting group
OL,21,Fwe've got."
