OL,3,CSteve Tandy: 'There's no magic wand or
OL,4,Cquick fix ` I believe in Welsh talent'
OL,6,FTandy won the Pro12 competition in six
OL,7,Fyears at Ospreys but left the Welsh
OL,8,Fregion in 2018.
OL,10,FHe worked for NSW Waratahs in
OL,11,FAustralia before moving to Scotland,
OL,12,Fwhile Gatland made him defence coach
OL,13,Fon the British and Irish Lions' 2021
OL,14,Ftour of South Africa.
OL,16,F"The one thing that has really driven
OL,17,Fme from the start is I want to be the
OL,18,Fbest person and the best coach I can
OL,19,Fpossibly be," Tandy said.
