OL,3,CSteve Tandy: 'There's no magic wand or
OL,4,Cquick fix ` I believe in Welsh talent'
OL,6,F"Did I ever think I'd be a Lions
OL,7,Fcoach? No. Did I ever think I'd coach
OL,8,Fthe Waratahs? No.
OL,10,F"But I think it's surprising what
OL,11,Fhappens when you have the mindset to
OL,12,Fbe better and to understand as well
OL,13,Fyou have got blind spots and you have
OL,14,Fgot things to work on."
OL,16,FTandy takes up his role on September 1
OL,17,Fand will prepare for autumn home games
OL,18,Fagainst Argentina, Japan, New Zealand
OL,19,Fand South Africa.
